## 2. ANDROID APP SIGNING

### Upload Key Setup
```bash
# Generate keystore
keytool -genkey -v -keystore upload-key.jks \
  -keyalg RSA -keysize 2048 -validity 10000 \
  -alias upload-key

# Configure flutter build
cd android
echo 'storeFile=../upload-key.jks' >> key.properties
echo 'storePassword=[PASSWORD]' >> key.properties
echo 'keyAlias=upload-key' >> key.properties
echo 'keyPassword=[PASSWORD]' >> key.properties
```

### Release Build
```bash
flutter build appbundle --release

# Output: build/app/outputs/bundle/release/app-release.aab
```

