## 3. GOOGLE PLAY BETA TESTING

### Internal Testing
- 5+ internal testers
- 1-2 days testing
- Crash validation
- Feature verification

### Closed Testing (Beta)
- Max 50,000 testers
- Public link distribution
- Gather user feedback
- Monitor crash reports
- Track ANRs

### Open Testing
- Unlimited testers
- Public visibility
- Pre-launch for production
- Final validation

