## 6. APP RELEASES

### Production Release
- âœ… Upload AAB file
- âœ… Set version name (1.0.0)
- âœ… Set version code (1)
- âœ… Write release notes
- âœ… Submit for review

### Review Timeframe
- Typical: 2-3 hours
- Range: 1-24 hours
- No formal review process
- Automated checks only

### Release Options

**Staged Rollout:**
- Start: 5% of users
- Monitor 24h
- Increase: 10% â†’ 25% â†’ 50% â†’ 100%
- Abort if >2% crash rate

**Immediate Release:**
- 100% rollout
- All users instantly
- No staged deployment

