## 7. VERSION MANAGEMENT

### Versioning Scheme

**Version Code:** Auto-increment (1, 2, 3, ...)
**Version Name:** Semantic versioning (1.0.0)

**Example:**
```
Version: 1.0.0, Code: 1 (initial release)
Version: 1.0.1, Code: 2 (bug fix)
Version: 1.1.0, Code: 3 (new features)
Version: 2.0.0, Code: 4 (major update)
```

