## 9. POST-LAUNCH MONITORING

### Google Play Console Metrics

**Installs:**
- Total installs
- Active installs
- Installation source
- Device types

**Ratings:**
- Star rating (1-5)
- Review count
- Recent reviews
- Review sentiment

**Crashes:**
- Crash rate %
- ANR rate %
- Affected users
- Stack traces
- Device/OS correlation

**Performance:**
- Startup time
- Memory usage
- Battery usage
- Crash trends

### Response Strategy

**Crash >0.5%:**
- Investigate immediately
- Fix and test
- Deploy hotfix
- Track regression

**Negative Reviews:**
- Respond within 24h
- Address concerns
- Offer solutions
- Request re-rating

**Feature Requests:**
- Categorize requests
- Prioritize by demand
- Plan roadmap
- Communicate timeline

---

## 10. UPDATE STRATEGY

### Critical Update (Emergency)
- Security vulnerability
- Major crash (>5%)
- Data loss bug
- Deploy immediately

### Bug Fix (Weekly)
- Non-critical bugs
- Performance improvements
- Minor UI fixes
- Deploy every Monday

### Feature Update (Bi-weekly)
- New features
- Major improvements
- UI/UX enhancements
- Deploy every other Friday

### Major Release (Quarterly)
- Significant features
- Architecture updates
- Major improvements
- Extended testing

